Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the depths' second layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've survived our final lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader, we pulled it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't really hit me yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we really get away from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to worry about anyone\Npursuing us anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry on, Reg.\NIt might be calling all of its buddies over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They must prepare themselves for what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In this place that transcends the ordinary,\Nthey themselves are outsiders,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the prey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These leaves sure are huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and the smell of the greenery has gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, while it's nice that the leaves help hide us,\Nthey totally block the view of our surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These trees might be big, but they're similar to amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Amagiri"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagiri sprouts always point\Ntoward the north of the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,just like these do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The branches similarly always point\Ntoward the center of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they're helpful when it's hard\Nto make out your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an old saying that goes:\N"If you get lost, just follow the amagiri."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you sound pretty smart right now, Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing like when we were back in Orth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... That's a compliment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to descend from around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We really need to head to Seeker Camp,\Nthe monitoring base down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's voice? This isn't like that other time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! There's somebody here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's crying for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Down on the ground there... It's a cave raider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drive that thing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, hold on! It could be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is a corpse-weeper...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They mimic the cries for help of prey they capture\Nto lure others to their colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means... that person is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one?! How careless of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's still in range!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't miss this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, unable to resist, goes down in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make those eyes shine brighter than a torch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The destination we are aiming for is deep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We squarely lose our way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap of the open-mouthed netherworld
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's chase the traces of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If an answer can be found now, we don't mind losing it all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The echo is still reverberating
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we do not part with that voice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The compass is always
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointed to the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where there is no escape
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is a curse
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse is the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will the yearning stop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ascending within the Abyss means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's being fed to the chicks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My body remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, I did something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... the strain of the second layer is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to lay her down quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If that thing had hit Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to be injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't wake up, so I got really worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but... you should stay lying down for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You were taking so long to wake up,\Nso I thought you might be hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And your clothes were all covered with vomit and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Reg,\Nyou don't need to act so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a robot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're the one who saved me, Reg, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of lost myself in the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think I ended up doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it must've come out of this spot on your hand here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what we should name it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Incinerator! Let's call this cannon thing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I very nearly completely blew you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg! It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, it was around...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,this big or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The size of the blast from your Incinerator\Nthe first time you saved me, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was from about 200 meters away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, you used to be able to control that power quite well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's train it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This power of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is something you can master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright? Reg?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Reg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone... Gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You suddenly fell asleep and\Nwouldn't wake up no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did firing your Incinerator tire you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, uh... fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Good to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what were you yelling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My cave-raiding notebook is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That notebook you were always making memos in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible I dropped it\Nwhen that corpse-weeper snatched me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The clasp on my pouch also got busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I had to lose it, I would've liked to have gotten\Nto the bottom of the netherworld first...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when it's found a long time from now,\Nit'll only contain my writings up till this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so my legend won't spread far and wide, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like: "Amazing! Riko totally made it\Nto the deepest depths!" Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"That Star Compass really was pointed\Nto the netherworld's bottom!" and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But you dropped that not too long ago, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I at least wanted to add something about your Incinerator\Nto my catalog of your features, Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my only regret...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite sure she also wrote something in there about\Nhow my penis looks like a real one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it stays hidden\Nin the netherworld's darkness for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a new one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried roasting it under some ouba leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept the seasoning simple and only used rock salt\Nand ground-up Eternal Fortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This... even looks tasty, doesn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum! It's got a delicious taste\Nthat appeals to the instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko! This is a bit peculiar but it's tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, you did well\Nto kill some game on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Reg, this is meat\Nfrom that corpse-weeper you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Riko, that doesn't bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpse-weepers sometimes eat humans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we just witnessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Reg, that still concerns you\Ndespite being a robot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably 'cause we both look generally the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we sometimes had meat\Nat the orphanage too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, most all of that stuff was hunted\Nby Blue Whistles in the first layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kinds of primeval creatures also feed on\Ncave raiders and ruffians to some degree or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad when they die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But they become the flesh and blood of those creatures,\Nand then once again become our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how we - all us cave raiders - have grown strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that scene that revisited me in a nightmare\Nis just part of daily life down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the resilience of those who live here\Nwas built up for the sake of life in the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the real thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The waterfalls are flowing upward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it won't shoot straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind here is blowing like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we can't keep taking shortcuts like we have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I feel like it somehow got colder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's windy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in the Inverted Forest, I wonder if we\Ndon't get that much light reflected by the force field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems pretty gloomy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? Want me to get out the cold-weather gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nah, we can't spread out our supplies here,\Nso later's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, hold this for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to make do with that until things settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, you're not cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel the wind, but no, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured as much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be borrowing this for now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg! Some kind of symbol appeared on your helmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I never noticed it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It never showed up while you were sleeping...\Nnot even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, maybe it's the writing system\Nthey use where you come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ah, it's disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I think they're called inbyos...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're saying, "This is our turf."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Think they're angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems we managed to make it out of their territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you're headed in the right direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, we should be able to see the route\Nto the Seeker Camper soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, right? I know where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One's a Red Whistle... and the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't even seem to be a cave raider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I ready the gondola?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling the wind's calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be because we've left\Nthe central part of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the creatures here\Nare more peaceful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The force field, you see, carries light and nutrients,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so there are more creatures\Nthe closer you get to the central shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I also hear that when you get farther away from there\Nthe Curse becomes a bit more bearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why the Seeker Camp is in\Nsuch a strangely remote place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inverted Forest is too high up\Nto descend from directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so it was originally built as a stopover point\Nfor people taking the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It just so happened that the location proved convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, long-range visibility is better\Nwhere the force field is weak, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So they ended up constructing a large telescope there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Seeker Camp, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really quite high up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Speaking of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the Seeker Camp always has a lookout on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So when someone starts approaching,\NI was told they lower the gondola for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A Red Whistle... A robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They might be feeling wary...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, are you able to stretch your arm up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe with both arms, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems I managed to re-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Something has...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,grabbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's still alive... that brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Unmovable Sovereign, Ozen the Immovable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a White Whistle who possesses\Nunrivaled physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That glint in her eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For these children, will it prove to be a glint of hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it instead an ominous omen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The glittering waves that float in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bundle them and build a rainbow bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous foothold, a slope we slide on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A signpost of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left hand, with my right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Join it, connect us, and let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am always beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, the present, and also the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's walk along without hesitating
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:23:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pile up multicolored dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will we head toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can be together with you, the world will begin to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's search for flowers that bloom at the ends of the earth
